sequenceDiagram
    participant "Kubernetes CronJob Scheduler" as KubernetesCronJobScheduler
    participant "DashboardMetricsCalculator Worker" as DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker
    participant "PostgreSQL Database (RDS)" as PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS

    activate DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker
    KubernetesCronJobScheduler->>DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker: 1. Triggers Pod creation based on cron schedule ('0 * * * *')
    DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker->>PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS: 2. BEGIN TRANSACTION (Isolation Level: Read Committed)
    PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS-->>DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker: Transaction context
    DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker->>PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS: 3. Execute optimized aggregation queries for all required metrics
    PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS-->>DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker: Aggregated data sets
    DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker->>PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS: 4. TRUNCATE TABLE "DashboardMetrics" and bulk INSERT new aggregated data
    PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS-->>DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker: Rows affected count
    DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker->>PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS: 5. COMMIT TRANSACTION
    PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS-->>DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker: Success confirmation
    DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker->>DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker: 6. Log successful execution with key metrics

    note over DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker: Error Handling Block: If any exception occurs during steps 3, 4, or 5, a catch block must execute...
    note over KubernetesCronJobScheduler: The Kubernetes CronJob spec MUST use a concurrencyPolicy of 'Forbid' or 'Replace' to prevent over...
    note over PostgreSQLDatabaseRDS: All aggregation queries must be analyzed with EXPLAIN ANALYZE to ensure they are using appropriat...

    deactivate DashboardMetricsCalculatorWorker
